Package com.brestats.model.data

Class DonneesAnnuelles

java.lang.Object
com.brestats.model.data.DonneesAnnuelles
All Implemented Interfaces:
Model
public class DonneesAnnuelles extends Object implements Model
The DonneesAnnuelles class represents annual data for a specific municipality and year. It implements the Model interface and provides methods to access and manipulate the annual data.

This class includes methods to get and set the number of houses, number of apartments, average price, average price per square meter, average surface area, total cultural expenses, total budget, and population.
